flowchart LR
  Inputs[Business/funnel/lead context] --> Brain[AI brain module]
  Brain --> Gateway[LLM gateway]
  Gateway -->|key present| Anthropic[Anthropic Messages API]
  Gateway -->|missing/failure| Fallback[Deterministic fallback]
  Anthropic --> Parser[JSON/schema parser]
  Fallback --> Output[Draft/report/recommendation]
  Parser --> Output
